  "text": "Antagomirs were designed as described [CITATION_1] . Briefly, RNA molecules 100% complementary to the mature miRNA to be antagonized were synthesized by Integrated DNA Technologies (IDT www.idtdna.com) with the following rules: a) .19nt length b) 39 Cholesterol moiety c) complete 29-O-methylation d) phosphorothioate linkage: first two nt at 59 end and 4 nt at 39 end. Specific sequences are shown in Table S2 . Lyophilized antagomiRs were reconstituted in H 2 O and directly added to the culture medium with at least dilutions of 1:50.",
